{
  // A search-tree node (SearchNode — never "Node": that name is the ENGINE object-type marker,
  // pre-set on every seeded node, which makes a so-named concept look already-cast on the first
  // pass and silently skips its children) — a kernel Thought carrying its MCTS stats as typed
  // facts: `visits`/`wins` (the driver backpropagates), `move` (the action that produced it),
  // `parent` (the edge). 0 is a valid visits value (require = resolvability, not truthiness).
  "require": ["Thought", "visits"]
}
